## Natural Diamond Presets Under $5,000

### Petite Solitaire — 1,020 Reviews · Most Popular

The Petite Solitaire is Blue Nile's best-selling preset. 1,020 reviews across the solitaire family confirms this is the highest-volume natural diamond engagement ring they sell at any price.

[![Blue Nile Round Diamond Petite Solitaire Yellow Gold Under 5000](/images/bn-u5k-rnd-yg-packshot.avif)](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/diamond-preset/round-1-ct-certified-diamond-petite-solitaire-engagement-ring-in-14k-yellow-gold-item-296972?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews)

**[Round 1ct Petite Solitaire in 14K White Gold](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/diamond-preset/round-1-ct-certified-diamond-petite-solitaire-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-item-296962?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $3,380 · 1,020 reviews · Item #296962**
GIA-certified 1ct round brilliant, petite four-prong setting in 14K white gold. The most-reviewed natural diamond preset in the catalog. For buyers who want a clean, classic solitaire at the lowest natural diamond price point Blue Nile offers. G or better color; VS2 or better clarity is typical for this preset tier.

**[Round 1ct Petite Solitaire in 14K Yellow Gold](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/diamond-preset/round-1-ct-certified-diamond-petite-solitaire-engagement-ring-in-14k-yellow-gold-item-296972?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $3,380 · 1,020 reviews · Item #296972**
Same 1ct round in yellow gold at the same price. The warm metal suits H color centers and gives the ring a distinctly warmer character. Same review count confirms equal purchase volume across both metals.

