### Petite Micropavé — 593 Reviews

**[Round 1ct Petite Micropavé in 14K White Gold](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/diamond-preset/round-1-ct-certified-diamond-petite-micropave-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-item-296982?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $3,730 · 593 reviews · Item #296982**
