### French Pavé — 476 Reviews · Closest to $5,000 for Natural

**[Round 1ct French Pavé in Platinum](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/diamond-preset/round-1-ct-certified-diamond-french-pave-engagement-ring-in-platinum-item-296888?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — $4,570 · 476 reviews · Item #296888**
The highest-priced natural diamond preset under $5,000. French pavé setting (V-shaped prongs between each pavé stone, allowing maximum light into the band diamonds) with a 1ct round center in platinum. 476 reviews at $4,570 confirms serious purchase intent. This is the most complete natural diamond ring Blue Nile sells under $5,000 — platinum construction, maximum band sparkle, GIA-certified center.

